## Responsive Design

### Breakpoint Strategy
- **Mobile-first**: Base styles for mobile devices
- **Tablet**: `md:` prefix for medium screens (768px+)
- **Desktop**: `lg:` prefix for large screens (1024px+)
- **Large Desktop**: `xl:` prefix for extra large screens (1280px+)

### Responsive Patterns
```typescript
// ✅ Good - Responsive layout changes
<div className="flex flex-column md:flex-row gap-3">
  {/* Stacks vertically on mobile, horizontally on desktop */}
</div>

// ✅ Good - Responsive grid columns
<div className="col-12 md:col-6 lg:col-4 xl:col-3">
  {/* 1 column on mobile, 2 on tablet, 3 on desktop, 4 on large desktop */}
</div>
```

