## Accessibility Styling

### Focus States
- **Visible focus indicators** for keyboard navigation
- **High contrast** for important interactive elements
- **Proper color contrast ratios** for text readability

### Screen Reader Support
```typescript
// ✅ Good - Proper ARIA labeling
<Image
  src={product.thumbnail}
  alt={product.title}
  aria-label={`Imagen del producto ${product.title}`}
/>
```

## Performance Considerations

### CSS Optimization
- **Use Tailwind's purge** to remove unused styles
- **Avoid custom CSS** unless absolutely necessary
- **Leverage PrimeReact's built-in styling** for components
- **Use CSS-in-JS sparingly** - prefer utility classes